<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF836A3CFBC394171ACAB95D" baseAuthorityName="Muller" baseAuthorityYear="1776" box="[1087,1226,590,623]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="120" pageNumber="878" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="borealis">L. borealis</taxonomicName>
and later considered a distinct species based on allozymes and restriction-enzyme analysis of mtDNA. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF836A3CFC6A94911A92B9D7" baseAuthorityName="Rhoads" baseAuthorityYear="1895" box="[918,1170,712,741]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="120" pageNumber="878" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="seminolus">Lasiurus seminolus</taxonomicName>
is in the Red Bat group. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
